{"tid":2290557,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"“平均每年升 n %” 呢個concept 到底係點嚟?","createTime":"2020-11-18T05:46:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T06:27:13.000Z","uid":201299,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"979a479f398517f36592cbf30089a02d72d98156","tid":2290557,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T05:46:13.000Z","msg":"喺Google打&ldquo;平均每年升&rdquo;/&ldquo;平均一年升&quot;<br />\n會見到好多新聞/資深投資專家都好鍾意話<br />\n&ldquo;過去十年間，A升咗n%，平均每年升 (n/10) %&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nE.g. A股價第一年升咗一倍，由100蚊升到200蚊，第二年由200升到400蚊，每年增幅一倍<br />\n但係好多新聞/專家就淨係將由100蚊到400蚊 (升300%)，講到平均每年增幅1.5倍，同實際增幅有好大出入<br />\n<br />\n到底 &ldquo;平均每年升n%&rdquo; 呢個concept 係點嚟?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ac821190c4aace849bcf736647afaeb1273f517","tid":2290557,"uid":14867,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T05:47:40.000Z","msg":"通常應該會講cagr 複合年增長？"},{"pid":"75b8d5edb2b11ff664b1bdd30eca539c8841d773","tid":2290557,"uid":73241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T05:47:43.000Z","msg":"geometric mean"},{"pid":"f5ec695ef183d57a3f28b25aca24d3ef91bb494a","tid":2290557,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T05:47:50.000Z","msg":"你睇下佢嘅讀者係咩人咪寫返咩level嘅嘢囉"},{"pid":"06ec6d73401cb031fb0f0a9923c06a08693dce68","tid":2290557,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T05:48:02.000Z","msg":"係用嚟昆傻散"},{"pid":"477c48a9ce85cb2b4bbad6b9f92d53a4529b0bfe","tid":2290557,"uid":198241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T05:49:43.000Z","msg":"林太：專家食屎"},{"pid":"a4ae40aded42b16b5e4aae70885157ddb0e4f878","tid":2290557,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T06:03:08.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">最難得是過去10年以來，集團累積升幅達13倍，平均每年升1.3倍，甚麼「股王」也難望其項背，令人感動！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surp